The Entrance to Crystal City~
Walking along the crystal path, a wall of crystal catches your eye.  The
wall is covered from base to top with precious gems, including diamonds,
rubies, emeralds, and sapphires, as well as gems unidentifiable to you. 
You realize that this wall must be one of the walls of the famous Crystal
city.  Set into the middle of the wall is a large gate, completely covered
in diamonds.  The gate is closed, but not locked.  The path leads north
into the city, or east, back to the main road. 
 
