The Crystal City Square~
As you walk further down the crystal road, you come upon the crystal
square.  Two crystal roads intersect each other here, the road on which
you were walking, and a smaller street that leads east and west of here.
Throughout the square, you see the citizens of this fine city, talking and
mingling about.  the most predominant feature of the square is a large
fountain made entirely of gold.  Crystal clear water spouts from the
fountain, spraying into the air with a cool mist, and landing back down
into the fountain again.  Roads lead in all directions from here.  North, the
road continues, the city gates are visible to the south, and  east and 
west a smaller road leads to the residential section of the city.
