Diamond Inn and Pub~
Stepping inside the pub, a sense of peace and security overwhelms you. 
This is a place where the citizens of Crystal City come to relax and have a
pint or two.  A cheery fireplace warms the room.  Several people are
gathered around the fire listening to an aged bard tell tales of his
adventures throughout the realm.  In one corner are three tables for people
to sit at and have a nice private conversation away from the hustle and
bustle of the pub.  Across from the set of tables is an ornately decorated
bar, made almost entirely of diamonds.  To the north of here is a set of
stairs that goes up to the second floor of the inn.  
