The Diamond Suite~
Entering the diamond suite, you gaze in awe at the marvelous sight; and
what a marvelous sight to behold.  The carpet is rich, plush, and luxuriant.
The walls are completely made from diamonds.  In one corner of the room is a
large bed, luxuriously' made up in crimson satin pillows, a crimson quilt,
and crimson satin sheets.  On either side of the bed are two large oak night
tables.  On either of the tables are a set of candles, all of which are lit,
providing a very romantic atmosphere.  Across from the bed is a closet, its
doors ornately adorned with gems of all types.  Inside the closet are
several richly made gowns, suits, and finely decorated formal wear.  The
only exit is back out to the hall.  
